::Striker::

Striker nods, looking around. "Ramulus has the complete programming of 
everything on the ship backed up, I believe."

He walks over to a charred console, sighing. "The Cybertronian Fire has spare 
comps, but this is Autobot technology, not Maximal. I doubt the two are 
compatible."
